##DESCRP=Chmod 000 chown nobody:nobody and add .OFF to files
function lockf() {
LOCKEDLOG=/root/support/.lockedf.`(date +"%m-%d-%Y")`

    if [ -z "$1" ]; then
        echo "Usage: lockf FILES";
        return;
    fi;
    until [ -z "$1" ]; do
	UGA=`stat -c "%U:%G:%a" $1`
        chmod 000 "$1";
        chown nobody:nobody "$1";
        mv "$1" "$1".OFF;
	echo "`pwd`$1 $UGA" >> $LOCKEDLOG
        shift;
    done
	echo "The following files have now been locked:"
	echo "--"
	cat $LOCKEDLOG
}

